Ojatykave'g̃a ndepiagame Jesus'ga g̃a porogwetygi. A'ereki g̃a he'ouhũ onhimongyavo tiruahũro g̃waramo ojive. Ndipokohavi g̃a no. Nahanahã g̃a ndekoi ovelhas ja – kiroki ovelhas ndogwerekoi gwepiakatuhara'ga.
